        "TileImage": "$($repository b89e5053-5bc1-4b6b-ab76-5c37f2994138).Image",
        "Description": "Good day 47,\rIt looks as though the current political climate has made the people of the USA a little on edge. They are quite literally at each others throats. Time to reap the rewards, so to speak. The targets today have each hired you to kill each other. They are convinced that their neighbors differing views have made them a threat. Lot of that going around these days. Ill leave you to prepare",
